	<conbody>
		<section id="xml_declaration_term">
			
			<p>An XML declaration is a processing instruction that identifies a document as XML.</p>
			
			<p>DITA documents must begin with an XML declaration.</p>
			<p>
				<b>Example</b>
			</p>
			<p>
				<codeblock>
&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?&gt;		
			</codeblock>
			</p>
		</section>
	</conbody>
